 time based fallback is managed from\nconfiguration parameters `retries` (default 5), and\n`base_retry_seconds` (default 0.5). Retry time doubles on each\nretry. E.g. try 0; wait 0.5s; try 1; wait 1s; try 2; wait 2s; try\n3; wait 4s; try 4; wait 8s; try 5; FAIL. Total time waited just\nunder base_retry_seconds * (2 \\*\\* retries).\n\n```\n.. automethod:: __init__\n```\n\n```\n.. automethod:: _rpc\n```\n\n```\n.. automethod:: close\n```\n"]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor", "documentation": ["!python", "-*- Python -*-"], "functions": [{"name": "cbor.cbor.dumps_int", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor._dumps_bignum_to_bytearray", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor._dumps_bignum_to_bytearray", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor.dumps_float", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor._encode_type_num", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cbor_type", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["For some CBOR primary type [0..7] and an auxiliary unsigned number, return CBOR encoded bytes"]}, {"name": "cbor.cbor._is_unicode", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor._is_unicode", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "cbor.cbor.dumps_string", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "val", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "is_text", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name":